\dfrac{1}{\sqrt{4\pi t}}\int_0^{\infty}ye^{-\frac{(\xi-y)^2}{4t}}dy
z=\dfrac{\xi-y}{2\sqrt t}
\text{erf}(\xi/(2\sqrt t)
 \int_{-\infty}^{\xi/(2\sqrt t)}(\xi-2\,\sqrt t\,z)e^{-z^2}\,dz=\xi\int_{-\infty}^{\xi/(2\sqrt t)}e^{-z^2}\,dz-2\,\sqrt t\int_{-\infty}^{\xi/(2\sqrt t)}z\,e^{-z^2}\,dz. 
